{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_710.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Looks like this month's bazaar is really flourishing. What should I buy today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wow, this butterfly necklace is so nice. But, I think it'll look better on Linca than on me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, maybe I'll buy it as a gift. She's been looking after me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you're right. This probably would look nice on her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, you think so, too, Linca? It looks so classy, it would be perfect for her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Wait, Linca!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x19c,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hello. Thanks for being friends with Linca."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you're welcome. Coming from Linca personally... Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "(There's something weird about this conversation... And something seems different about her...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It'd make me happy if you'd keep being good friends with Linca. I'm counting on you, Ayesha cupcake."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Oh, y-yes...<CR>Ayesha cupcake...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "These were favorable circumstances. We were able to get a great deal on fresh vegetables."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That's a relief. With our low salaries, we can't afford to spend a lot of money on food."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Tonight, I will try my best to prepare scrambled eggs!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "How can you cook eggs when we only bought vegetables?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Marion and...Linca!? Wh-Whaaat!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Ayesha, what's wrong? What're you yelling for?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Oh, well, umm, I, necklace, and Linca, was a gift, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Okay, stop! I can't understand what you're saying."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Calm down, and take a deep breath. Okay, iiin, and ooout, iiiiiin, and oooooout."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "O-Okay, iiin, and ooout, iiiiiin, and oooooout."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Better now? Okay, start talking."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Well, when I was shopping just now, Linca was talking to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "But another Linca came from that side with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Marion...it seems like Linca is here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Seems so. To chase us down to this frontier... She doesn't give up, does she?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm, I totally have no clue about what's going on..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Right, I'm sorry. Since you've met Linca, I guess I have to explain everything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "It's kind of complicated, so do you think you can come by my office later?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I do not want to cause trouble for Ayesha, but...please do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(I should go to her office later. They both had such serious expressions...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "(Anyway, two Lincas...<CR>What's going on...!?)"
        }
    ]
}